20 . More recent influences have included the American film actress  Joan Crawford  (  1908–77 , born  Lucille le Sueur ), the British actress  Joan Collins  (  b. 1933 ), the American comedienne  Joan Rivers  (  b. 1933 ), and the West Indian pop singer  Joan Armatrading  (  b. 1950 )."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["form of   John  , also used quite frequently in the English-speaking world. In Northern Ireland it is sometimes found as a variant of   Ewan ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Joan had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Henry Cantalupe."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1465–Female":"1465–Surnud","–1517":"–1517","–Female":"Surnud","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","1517":"1517","1490":"1490","Collingtree, Northamptonshire, England":"Collingtree, Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1465–Female":"1465–Kuollut","–1517":"–1517","–Female":"Kuollut","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","1517":"1517","1490":"1490","Collingtree, Northamptonshire, England":"Collingtree, Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1465–Female":"1465–Décédée","–1517":"–1517","–Female":"Décédée","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","1517":"1517","1490":"1490","Collingtree, Northamptonshire, England":"Collingtree, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Joan a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille avec Henry Cantalupe."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1465–Female":"1465–Verstorben","–1517":"–1517","–Female":"Verstorben","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","1517":"1517","1490":"1490","Collingtree, Northamptonshire, England":"Collingtree, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Joan hatte mit Henry Cantalupe mindestens 1 Sohn und 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1465–Female":"1465–Desede","–1517":"–1517","–Female":"Desede","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","1517":"1517","1490":"1490","Collingtree, Northamptonshire, England":"Collingtr